parameters: \nc<>Is this your base? It's decorated so nicely.

\TA[1]Cashew Nut gave it to me when I said I wanted to have a
secret meeting like adults!
\TA[1]The name of the mascot that we made a contract with.
\TA[1]Levantia has one too, right? A mascot.

\TA[1]Ah, ah... well, that's right. Haha. We're a little apart
right now though.
\TA[1]If you find that cat, it won't be just a simple matter.

\TA[1](...Huh? Come to think of it, this feeling of magic...)
Feels familiar...
\TA[1]H-Hello. It's been a while, Levantia. Meow~

\TA[1]So it's you after all, Nyanko. To boldly show your face
again.

\TA[1](M-My face...!) (Wait, wait! The underclassmen are
watching, meow!)

\TA[1]Um, um, Levantia-san and Cashew Nut-chan... are you
acquainted?
\TA[1]Y-Yes, that's right, meow! To be honest...

\TA[1]Kei, in other words, I'm the one who turned Levantia into a
magical girl, meow!

\TA[1]...That's right. I used to work together with this person
before. Although the location is a little far from here.
\TA[1](The pure gaze of the two of them hurts...)
\TA[1]S-So, did I not say that I have something to talk about?
\TA[1]Ah, that's right! Thank you so much for helping me earlier.

\TA[1]If it wasn't for Levantia-san, I would have had a serious
injury.
\TA[1]I hate pain... Thank you so much for helping me, Kei.

\TA[1]I said it earlier, but don't worry about it. Thanks to
that, we discovered such an amazing coincidence, right?
\TA[1]Ah, so what is it that you wanted to talk about?

\TA[1]It's my turn to speak, meow. I'll get straight to the point,
meow.
\TA[1]...I can't do that. You understand, right?

\TA[1]If we leave everything to someone else, these children will
remain weak forever.

\TA[1]But the current situation is abnormal, meow. The villains
are becoming strong at an incredibly fast speed.

\TA[1]If we leave it like this, these children will be defeated
before they become strong, meow.

\TA[1](That's true, the muscle daruma earlier was strangely
strong.) (It's a good thing it was me as the opponent, but
if it were these children...)

\TA[1]Please, meow. I'm not asking for everything, meow. Just
until these children become strong is enough, meow...!
\TA[1]Okay, I got it, so please lift your head. I'm really weak when it comes to that kind of thing...

\TA[1](What should I do? I didn't want to be a magical girl
anymore.)

\TA[1](But if we leave it like this, those children might
experience the same thing again today.) (I can't just
pretend I don't know that...)
カシューナッツの提案を受け入れる｡
\TA[1]I understand. I will accept your request.

\TA[1]As expected of Levantia, I believed in you, meow! I've
always thought that Levantia is a capable child--
\TA[1]I-Is it okay? Even if we end up in danger because of us...
\TA[1]It's okay. In a way, I'm used to it.

\TA[1]And also, since I'll be taking care of those unruly ones in
your place, make sure to become stronger quickly, okay?
\TA[1]...! Yes, I will do my best!

\TA[1]Alright, since we've become colleagues, is there anything
you want to ask?
How can I become so strong?
Are there any other magical girls?
ヴィランって何ですか？

\TA[1]No, no, no! I explained it properly, meow! I didn't deceive
you into making a contract, meow!
\TA[1]Villains, evil beings that come from another world.

\TA[1]In order to completely purify and not just temporarily
eliminate, a magical girl with the same power from another
world is necessary.
\TA[1]Oh, you remember Sherbet well. Good job, good job.

\TA[1]Pink Candy, please study a little harder, meow. No, I mean
it seriously...
どうすればそんなに強くなれるの？

\TA[1]Me? Well, I've had various things happen to me, or
rather...

\TA[1]I'm Levantia, the magical girl of Mile City! Everyone's
happiness is my responsibility--

\TA[1]Ahem. To answer seriously, magical girls become stronger
based on the emotions they receive from people.

\TA[1]In short, it means that if you help many people and get
along with everyone, you can become stronger, meow!
\TA[1]...I wonder if everyone is doing well.
他に魔法少女はいないの？

\TA[1]I hate to bring it up, but are you the only magical girls
around here?

\TA[1]When I was active, the magical girls nearby would help each
other.

\TA[1]I've heard that they exist. But it seems like everyone is
busy...

\TA[1]Famous magical girls go to Tokyo. Non-famous magical girls
are busy in their own cities. Everyone is desperate.

\TA[1]The recent kids seem to be going through a lot. We can't
really increase their numbers either.
\TA[1]Magical girls with talent are not easily found, meow.

\TA[1]And yet, they say we're slow in searching from above, or
that we should stop sticking to the girls' sides and start
walking around...
\TA[1](I didn't mean it in that way...)

\TA[1](But, maybe it wasn't just a coincidence that I reunited
with this person.)
\TA[1]W-What's wrong, meow!? Is your wound not healed?
\TA[1]Uh-oh. I'm going to get scolded by Papa...

\TA[1]Ahaha. Well, let's stop here for today then.
Is there
anything else you want to talk about?
\TA[1]Hmm, there is something, but... it's not urgent, meow.

\TA[1]Alright, let's meet again tomorrow or the day after
tomorrow.
\TA[1]Kei obtained the key to the secret base!

\TA[1]With this, you can enter here. Levantia-san, feel free to
use it anytime!

\TA[1]Thank you. And please continue to take care of me from now
on. Until you all become stronger, that is.
